<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.7.2">
<l>vāyilpal lumeḻunti lamayirum muṭikū ṭiṟṟila</l>
<l>cāyvilā takuṟunta laiccila piḷḷai kaḷōṭiṇaṅki</l>
<l>tīyiṇak kiṇaṅkā ṭivantivaḷ taṉṉaṉṉa cemmaicolli</l>
<l>māyaṉmā maṇivaṇṇaṉ mēlivaḷ mālu ṟukiṉṟāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Her] teeth do not rise above [her] lips!</l>
<l rend="indent">[Her] hair hasn’t gathered into a knot!</l>
<l>Having befriended a few girls with little heads</l>
<l rend="indent">that do not bow [with modesty],</l>
<l>consenting to ruinous liasons,</l>
<l rend="indent">she wanders back speaking as honourably as usual,</l>
<l>She is suffering from a delusion about the great jewel toned Māyaṉ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
